{"tid":1542731,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"連登筆友計劃2019","createTime":"2019-09-05T02:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T17:41:13.000Z","uid":96387,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bc1e113c285dbf310f1bafb70d8a8823f638c542","tid":1542731,"uid":96387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:53:26.000Z","msg":"對上一次嘅連登筆友計劃,已經係2017嘅事，近排香港發生左太多嘅事，我相信大家都好攰好多野都想搵人傾，所以想搞一次筆友計劃，等大家發夢完果時都可以同人傾下，抒發下感情<br />\n建議真係有心寫長信既人先好交表，如果只係想識人，我諗其他TG Post 會更適合你地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">樓主溫馨提示:網上世界好得人驚，切勿與初相識嘅人透露太多犯法嘢</span><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">交表前記得睇左呢度先!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n0. 份Form 嘅問題唔好留空太多，我會跟你填嘅野做配對<br />\n<br />\n1. 每人獲配兩異性一同性;<br />\n而同時Admin會將你地分配俾其他巴絲打, 所以會有其他人主動Approach嘅情況出現, 各位唔需要大驚少怪 <br />\n<br />\n例: 假設A係其一參加人，佢會收到B、C、D嘅資料做佢嘅筆友（兩異性一同性），而A嘅資料亦都會send去E,F,G到做另一個配對。<br />\n<br />\n2. 每個email只可以交表 1 次<br />\n(筆友唔啱你可以email我, 會再配俾你, 唔洗玩分身, 見者即block)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n表格:<a href=\"https://forms.gle/boKnfuowGUPZN8XK9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FboKnfuowGUPZN8XK9&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=267bc6b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/boKnfuowGUPZN8XK9</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">截Form時間:<br />\n9 月 11 日 (三), 晚上 11時59分</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">配對時間:<br />\n9 月 12 日開始陸續配對同send 配對 email<br />\n希望中秋前可以send 哂啲 email 出去</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">個post 有參考到之前連登筆友計劃嘅格式，如果post 主介意可以留言講返</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9ed686bc57fbab69a9f06adf352b5bb9e4e724c","tid":1542731,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"116e5bbafc40771d11b453ac730694c498f36026","tid":1542731,"uid":96387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51adbbe816fb82354bf3d0f73430f27ddb8b0ad3","tid":1542731,"uid":71292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6601198848071b7a08620951f6f546ac07b5bbb3","tid":15427